strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_TWINSBLESSING_KEYWOR: <style=cKeywordName><color=#00BDFF>Atuykarounkami's Blessings</color></style><style=cSub>On impact, create a <style=cIsDamage>tidal blast</style> on nearby surface that deals <style=cIsDamage>210% damage</style>
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_TWINSCURSE3_KEYWORD: <style=cKeywordName><color=#711fa3>Shadow Vulnerability</color></style><style=cSub>Increase <color=#711fa3>Hex</color> duration and <style=cIsDamage>additively</style> increase <color=#711fa3>Hex</color> damage with each stack.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_TWINSRAYCAST_KEYWORD: <style=cKeywordName><style=cIsDamage>Tiriryarai</style></style><style=cSub>Skill activates at your <style=cIsUtility>crosshair's location</style> with <style=cIsUtility>no travel time</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_TWINSWIND_KEYWORD: <style=cKeywordName><color=#0b9c2d>Wind God's Perfect Defense</color></style><style=cSub>Block most attacks while channeling</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_PASSIVE_NAME: Ever Turning, Ever Swaying, Ever Drifting
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_PASSIVE_DESCRIPTION: Ururuu and Saraana have independent loadouts and <style=cIsUtility>switch turns</style> upon reaching maximum <color=#EDA717>Zeal</color>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_PRIMARY0_DESCRIPTION: Fire a <color=#4d108f>shadow sphere</color> for <style=cIsDamage>320% damage</style> that <style=cIsDamage>explodes</style> on impact. Hold up to 4.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_PRIMARY1_DESCRIPTION: Hold to repeatedly fire tracking <color=#4d108f>energy bolts</color> for <style=cIsDamage>120% damage</style>. Continous fire will charge a <color=#4d108f>shadow sphere</color> that can be released for <style=cIsDamage>550% damage</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_PRIMARY2_DESCRIPTION: <style=cIsDamage>Tiriryarai</style>. Hold to sow <color=#4d108f>seeds of darkness</color>. Release to <color=#4d108f>harvest</color> for <style=cIsDamage>175% damage</style> plus an additional <style=cIsDamage>250% damage</style> per <color=#4d108f>seed</color>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_PRIMARY3_DESCRIPTION: Conjure 4 powerful <color=#4d108f>shadowflames</color> that deal <style=cIsDamage>100% damage</style> each and <color=#711fa3>Hex</color> enemies.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_SECONDARY1_DESCRIPTI: <style=cIsDamage>Stunning</style>. Conjure a boulder for <style=cIsDamage>460% damage</style> that splinters into smaller debris for <style=cIsDamage>230% damage</style> each.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_SECONDARY0_DESCRIPTI: <style=cIsDamage>Ignite</style>. Charge up a slow-moving molten ball that <style=cIsDamage>scorches</style> nearby enemies for <style=cIsDamage>150%-250% damage</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_SECONDARY3_DESCRIPTI: <style=cIsUtility>Freezing</style>. Summon a pillar of ice to periodically damage nearby enemies for <style=cIsDamage>100% damage</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_SECONDARY2_DESCRIPTI: <color=#0b9c2d>Wind God's Perfect Defense</color>. Fire a slicing blade of wind that rapidly strikes enemies for <style=cIsDamage>250% damage</style> or fully charge to <style=cIsUtility>decrease all your cooldowns</style> by <style=cIsUtility>2.5s</style> and gain a speed boost.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_SECONDARY4_DESCRIPTI: <style=cIsDamage>Tiriryarai</style>. <style=cIsHealth>10% HP</style>. Call down a star from the heavens that deals <style=cIsDamage>950% damage</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_UTILITY0_DESCRIPTION: <style=cIsDamage>Tiriryarai</style>. Strike an enemy with lightning for <style=cIsDamage>900% damage</style> and additionally create <style=cIsDamage>3</style> aftershocks that seek enemies for <style=cIsDamage>750% damage</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_UTILITY1_DESCRIPTION: Fire a series of water bolts that deal <style=cIsDamage>250% damage</style> each. The number of bolts fired increases with attack speed. <style=cIsDamage>Critical Strikes</style> become <color=#00BDFF>Atuykarounkami's Blessings</color>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_UTILITY2_DESCRIPTION: <style=cIsDamage>Tiriryarai</style>. Call for the Mirage Blade's assistance. His afterimages rapidly strike foes for <style=cIsDamage>130% damage</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_UTILITY3_DESCRIPTION: Produce a <style=cIsUtility>miasma</style> at the targeted area. Enemies that die inside the <style=cIsUtility>miasma</style> have their souls <style=cIsUtility>bound to you</style> temporarily.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_SPECIAL0_DESCRIPTION: Unleash a <color=#4d108f>great roar of darkness</color> for <style=cIsDamage>12,500% total damage</style>. Surviving enemies are <style=cIsDamage>marked for death</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_SPECIAL1_DESCRIPTION: Mark an area to be sealed after <style=cIsUtility>2.5s</style>. Once primed, the seal activates, dealing <style=cIsDamage>650% damage</style>. <style=cIsHealth>ALL living things</style> below <style=cIsHealth>20% health</style> are <style=cIsDamage>executed</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_SPECIAL2_DESCRIPTION: Manifest a <color=#4d108f>dark star</color> to continually <color=#711fa3>Hex</color> enemies each interval and apply <color=#711fa3>Shadow Vulnerability</color>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_EXTRA1_DESCRIPTION: <style=cIsUtility>Disappear</style> into the aether and become <style=cIsUtility>invulnerable</style> for a short time.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_EXTRA2_DESCRIPTION: <style=cIsDamage>Stunning</style>. Deal <style=cIsDamage>175% damage</style>, briefly <style=cIsUtility>disappear</style>, and then <style=cIsUtility>reappear</style> in a nearby location.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_EXTRA4_DESCRIPTION: Call <style=cIsDamage>Mothmoth</style> to the battlefield. He grants <style=cIsHealth>lifesteal</style> to all allies around him.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_EXTRA3_DESCRIPTION: <style=cIsUtility>Push</style> away all nearby enemies and weave an <style=cIsUtility>impermeable barrier</style> that lasts <style=cIsUtility>15 seconds</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_EXTRA5_DESCRIPTION: Summon a primeval spirit of <style=cIsDamage>War</style>, <style=cIsHealing>Decay</style>, or <style=cIsHealth>Mischief</style> to attack your enemies.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_EXTRA6_DESCRIPTION: Offer <style=cIsHealth>25% of your life force</style> in a prayer to <style=cIsDamage>Lord Mashiro</style>. Once finished, you are granted a <style=cIsDamage>blessing</style> for the next <style=cIsUtility>30 seconds</style>. If you <style=cIsHealth>perish</style> while under the effect of a <style=cIsDamage>blessing</style>, you are <style=cIsDamage>reincarnated</style>. <style=cIsUtility>Taking damage will interrupt the prayer</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_EXTRA7_DESCRIPTION: Summon a <style=cIsDamage>profane coagulation</style> that stuns enemies and <style=cIsUtility>inflicts debuffs</style> the <style=cIsHealth>closer it gets to death</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_EXTRA8_DESCRIPTION: Consume a kuko fruit to <style=cIsDamage>instantly</style> gain maximum <color=#EDA717>Zeal</color>.
